{"tid":888844,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界最成功嘅八十後","createTime":"2018-11-04T06:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T06:09:58.000Z","uid":15935,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d688d83a283124ba35128c4231a69ef9edfb97c6","tid":888844,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"除咗金委員長之外，我諗唔到第二個人成就高得過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n30歲人，就憑一人之力能夠玩到中美兩個陀陀擰，成日搞到日本淆底，可見政治智慧之高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毒殺呀哥，犬決呀叔，展示過人嘅膽量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n三兩下手勢就快搞掂老竇呀爺成世人都處理唔到嘅朝鮮半島統一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一年用唔知幾多百億買來佬高級貨自己用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b81aa7219bdad66b831df720c86b650f56ca851","tid":888844,"uid":200247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"哦"}]}